CFP®, Savant Capital Management Rebecca Epperson, Chartwell Agency Mike Fager, CFP ® , Raymond James & Associates William Gorski, MD Paul Green, CIMC®, CIMA®, Wells Fargo Advisors Curtis D. Kleckler, CPA, Benning Group, LLC Stephen Minore, MD, FCCP, FICS, CPE, Rockford Anesthesiologists Associated Matt Roegner, Banking Executive Dave Rydell, Bergstrom, Inc. Pamela Schmidt, DDS Christie Jarrett, Stenstrom Companies Ltd Kristoffer Tumilowicz, DMD, Dental Dimensions EX OFFICIO MEMBERS Terri Blevins, EdD, UI-COMR, ex officio Carrie Hermanson, UI-COMR, ex officio Teresa Johnston, UI-COMR, ex officio Mitch King, MD, UI-COMR, ex officio Laura Knight, MBA, UI-COMR, ex officio Connie Vitali, MD, UI-COMR, ex officio  DAC COMMITTEES Board Recruitment Committee Elise Cadigan, LCSW Gary Kaatz Craig Fetty, CFP ®, Mike Fager, CFP ®, Development Committee Not currently active Student Involvement Committee Elise Cadigan, LCSW William Gorski, MD Joshua Baalman, M3 – President Aisha Bhatti, M2 – Vice President Christina Tsai, M3 – Treasurer Aubrey Graham, M3 – Secretary M1 rep to be named in August Dr. Alex Stagnaro-Green  Regional Dean About Welcome From Regional Dean Dean’s Action Council Fast Facts UIC Health Sciences Campus Glenn Netto Health & Wellness Center Visiting the Campus Employment Apply for a Job at the College Civil Service Practice Test Benefits Discover Rockford Contact Us About  Education  Research  Patient Care  Departments  News  Giving INFORMATION FOR: Prospective and Current Students  Faculty & Staff  Alumni & Friends  Patients  Businesses and Community RESOURCES: UIC Directory  Blackboard  Emergency Information  Contact Us  Apply Now  Give  Contact Us Connect with us!    If you have questions, comments, or problems accessing this site, please E-mail the webmaster  © Copyright 2019 University of Illinois College of Medicine   | Privacy Statement College of Medicine | Chicago | Peoria | Rockford | Urbana                                                                                                                                             